1. Ja ću *pošaljem* pismo sutra. (I will send the letter tomorrow.)
2. Ona *pošalje* mejl svom šefu svaki dan. (She sends an email to her boss every day.)
3. Da li si *poslao* mejl svojim kolegama? (Did you send an email to your colleagues?)
4. Kada budeš *poslao* poruku, javi mi. (When you send a message, let me know.)
5. On je *poslao* paket preko pošte. (He sent a package via the post office.)
6. Oni *poslaše* telegram da su stigli na odredište. (They sent a telegram saying they had arrived at their destination.)
7. Molim vas da *pošaljete* svoje prijave do petka. (Please send your applications by Friday.)
8. Ti *pošalji* poruku kada stigneš kući. (Send a message when you get home.)